p.k: Puppycorn is determined to become the Hot Dog King and joins an underground hot dog eating contest called Weiner Club. / During a fun fireworks show, Unikitty and Master Frown become trapped in the horn of the Unikitty Castle when she catches Master Frown messing with her fireworks. / Puppycorn is determined to become the Hot Dog King and joins an underground hot dog eating contest called Weiner Club. / When Master Frown starts ruining parties to earn a promotion from his bosses, the Doom Lords, Brock accidentally gets blamed for the calamity. / Puppycorn is sick of Unikitty always helping him out and doesn't want to be the "little" brother anymore.
